Name: Google Sheets - Search
Description: Searches for a Google Sheet Spreadsheet by name
Params: name: The partial or full name of the spreadsheet to search for
Share Tools: github.com/otto8-ai/tools/google/sheets
Type: input

#!/bin/env bash

cat << EOF

Use the Google Sheets listSpreadsheets tool to find the spreadsheet specified within these <input> tags: <input>${NAME}</input>.
Remember the ID of this spreadsheet, but only return the full name to the user.

EOF

